WEBVTT

00:01:27.013 --> 00:01:30.471
The overwhelming majority
of all species and all civilizations

00:01:30.495 --> 00:01:31.665
that have ever existed

00:01:31.689 --> 00:01:32.998
are now history.

00:01:33.022 --> 00:01:35.871
And if we want to be
the exception to that,

00:01:35.895 --> 00:01:41.808
then logically, our only hope
is to make use of the one feature

00:01:41.832 --> 00:01:46.458
that distinguishes our species
and our civilization from all the others;

00:01:46.482 --> 00:01:51.791
namely, our ability to create
new explanations, new knowledge,

00:01:51.815 --> 00:01:54.535
to be a hub of existence.

00:01:55.165 --> 00:01:59.577
CA: David's thinking about knowledge
has had a huge impact on me personally.

